OL,7,Fstabbed to death at a party in Bath
OL,8,Fhas shared her heartbreaking memory of
OL,9,Fthe moment she found out her son had
OL,10,Fbeen killed.
OL,12,F, was stabbed in the neck with a large
OL,13,Fzombie knife during a fight which
OL,14,Fbroke out at the party on 10 June 2023.
