OL,3,C'I had 37 missed calls then I fell on
OL,4,Cthe floor' - Mum of boy killed at party
OL,6,FHayley and her mother, who was also at
OL,7,Fthe ball, travelled back to Bristol
OL,8,Fwith a friend.
OL,10,FShe says she had hoped Mikey was
OL,11,Fsimply injured, but when she was
OL,12,Fdiverted to the scene in Bath, she
OL,13,Fknew his friends had been telling her
OL,14,Fthe truth.
OL,16,F"I didn't know what to do", Hayley
OL,17,Ftold ITV News.
OL,19,F"I think I just fell on the floor. You
OL,20,Fdon't feel like you live in the real
OL,21,Fworld.
