OL,3,C'I had 37 missed calls then I fell on
OL,4,Cthe floor' - Mum of boy killed at party
OL,6,F"I've been left with nightmares most
OL,7,Fnights. The only way to deal with it,
OL,8,Fis you hope it is going to go back to
OL,9,Fnormal. I know it's not, but I just
OL,10,Fmiss him."
OL,12,FHayley told ITV News about the gaping
OL,13,Fhole he has left in her family's life
OL,14,Fand her determination to not let
OL,15,Fothers suffer in the same way.
OL,17,FShe said: "I cannot believe kids carry
OL,18,Fthese (zombie) knives around with
OL,19,Fthem. Where do they get them from? We
OL,20,Fcan't keep doing this.
