OL,3,C'I had 37 missed calls then I fell on
OL,4,Cthe floor' - Mum of boy killed at party
OL,6,F"Kids are killing kids. Something has
OL,7,Fto change. Every time it happens
OL,8,Fagain, I just think their poor mother,
OL,9,Fsome other family has to go through
OL,10,Fthis again.
OL,12,F"I'd like to see tougher sentences for
OL,13,Fpeople carrying knives and stop and
OL,14,Fsearch should be used more, it might
OL,15,Fjust make people think twice about
OL,16,Fcarrying a weapon."
OL,18,FMikey has been described as a kind,
OL,19,Fpopular and fearless teenager who
OL,20,Floved spending time with his friends
OL,21,Fand who had recently started rapping.
