OL,6,FHe died before he could collect his
OL,7,FGCSEs which he went on to pass.
OL,9,FHayley has since set up the charity
OL,10,FMikey's World and has fundraised money
OL,11,Fto purchase more than a hundred bleed
OL,12,Fkits for the community and provide
OL,13,Ftraining for youngsters in how to use
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FShe said: "If we can get kids to see -
OL,17,Fif you choose to do this to somebody,
OL,18,Fsomeone could die in three minutes and
OL,19,Fwhat you need to do to save them, then
OL,20,Fmaybe it will encourage kids not to
OL,21,Fcarry knives."
